cast.overview: A look at the relationship between Mike and Sulley during their days at Monsters University — when they weren't necessarily the best of friends.
cast.title: Monsters University

details.biography: Pam Murphy is an American actress, voice actress, writer, and comedian. She trained with the Upright Citizens Brigade and has appeared in Get Shorty, Night Court, Mapleworth Murders, Single Parents, Superstore, Crazy Ex-Girlfriend, Another Period, and Key & Peele. She voices Stupendous in Krapopolis, the FOX animated series created by Dan Harmon.
details.name: Pam Murphy
